    <article>
        <p><img src="images/2020-06-12-08-39-31.png" alt="2020-06-12-08-39-31.png" style="max-width: 100%;" /></p>
<p>A lot of stocks are really down, some much more than average: Cruise ships, amusement parks, Dave and Busters, movie theater chains.</p>
<p>Selling all of my stock index funds and buying up whatever is cheap.</p>
<p>UPDATE 2 years later: everything went great :D</p>

